  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Idle weapon collection and weapon development game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Idle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automatically acquire weapons, my room, jukebox, game money, and more.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Weapon</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automatically acquire weapons based on rarity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rarity: Common, Rare, Legendary</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maximum Level: 9999</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A legendary weapon with distinctive effects displayed as it is upgraded</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Feed</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automatically acquire feed based on rarity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rarity: Common, Rare, Legendary</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Used for weapon level-up</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>My Room</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automatically acquire my room based on rarity</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rarity: Common, Rare, Legendary</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Background with various themes</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Jukebox</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automatically acquire the jukebox based on rarity</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rarity: Common, Rare, Legendary</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soundtrack with various atmospheres</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Shop</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >General Shop: Allows purchase of common and rare items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Legendary Shop: Allows purchase of legendary items</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Controls</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fullscreen/Windowed mode: F4 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Default key: Arrow Keys, Enter, Esc, Mouse  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keybinding support</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take care of the weapon like a baby. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It gets hungry and poops.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Legendary weapons can be automatically obtained.</p>",
